{"tid":1380003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"袋棍球","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:28:49.000Z","uid":216178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b866c13387ef70a389a140e1fd32ce880586b26f","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"袋棍球（Lacrosse），又譯長曲棍球、曲棍網球、棍網球、兜網球、袋球或網棒球，是一種使用頂端具有網狀袋子的長棍作為持球工具的團隊球類運動。起源於北美原住民部落，原本不限人數，<span style=\"color: red;\">最多可達雙方各一千餘人</span>。移民至此的法國人發現後，加以改良並制訂規則，因而形成今日的狀態。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzwVhac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzwVhac.jpg&h=1d492776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzACvve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzACvve.jpg&h=5bbe6925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港千人比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa1f9b9c5cabc7775f9c1ded0a14533ddd2a8be","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"用途多多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c96a322b74779843a8f8b040c57f73450837d9","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:07:28.000Z","msg":"居家旅行必備"},{"pid":"b54072a2ba5f98ebc240fb805fbf3cf692d48ed9","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a449765082ef8df1abae1209437d6b2d8a132b","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1637197cd78dd6e7218380416454a5929f38b5","tid":1380003,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm